animeDescription: The story will center around a protagonist who goes to Powerful High School to achieve his dreams of being a baseball player. There, he reunites with a childhood friend named Subaru Hoshii, who he promised to play at the Summer Koshien high school championship game with in the past, but who seems to have forgotten their promise.(Source: ANN)
animeStaff: [['Watanabe, Tetsuaki', 'Director'], ['Itou, Takumi', 'Sound Director'], ['Ooishi, Masayoshi', 'Theme Song Performance'], ['Tsubone, Kentarou', 'Editing']]
